<leg:levelstatus isrepealed="false" ln.user-displayed="false"/></leg:levelinfo>
<leg:heading><desig searchtype="DIV-NUM"><designum><refpt id="UCPN.OL.FOEA94.PT3.D2" type="ext"/>DIVISION 2</designum></desig><title searchtype="DIV-TITLE">OBTAINING FOREIGN MATERIAL [ss 21&#x2013;23]</title></leg:heading>
<leg:levelbody>
<leg:level id="UCPN.OL.FOEA94.S21"><leg:level-vrnt leveltype="sect" searchtype="LEGISLATION SECT" subdoc="true" toc-caption="[320,240] s 21 Requests for foreign material">
<leg:levelinfo>
<leg:levelstatus isrepealed="false" ln.user-displayed="false"/></leg:levelinfo>
<leg:heading inline="true"><edpnum><refpt id="UCPN.OL.FOEA94.S21" type="ext"/>[320,240]</edpnum><title searchtype="SECT-TITLE">Requests for foreign material</title><desig searchtype="SECT-NUM"><designum>21</designum></desig></leg:heading>
<leg:levelbody>
<leg:bodytext>
<p><text>This Part applies to testimony, and any exhibit annexed to such testimony, obtained as a result of a request made by or on behalf of the Attorney-General to a foreign country for the testimony of a person, and any exhibit annexed to such testimony, to be made available.</text></p>
</leg:bodytext>
</leg:levelbody>
</leg:level-vrnt>
</leg:level>
<leg:level id="UCPN.OL.FOEA94.S22"><leg:level-vrnt leveltype="sect" searchtype="LEGISLATION SECT" subdoc="true" toc-caption="[320,245] s 22 Requirements for testimony">
<leg:levelinfo>
<leg:levelstatus isrepealed="false" ln.user-displayed="false"/></leg:levelinfo>
<leg:heading inline="true"><edpnum><refpt id="UCPN.OL.FOEA94.S22" type="ext"/>[320,245]</edpnum><title searchtype="SECT-TITLE">Requirements for testimony</title><desig searchtype="SECT-NUM"><designum>22</designum></desig></leg:heading>
<leg:levelbody>
<leg:level id="UCPN.OL.FOEA94.S22.1"><leg:level-vrnt leveltype="subsect" searchtype="LEGISLATION SUBSECT">
<leg:levelinfo>
<leg:levelstatus isrepealed="false" ln.user-displayed="false"/></leg:levelinfo>
<leg:heading inline="true"><desig><designum><refpt id="UCPN.OL.FOEA94.S22.1" type="ext"/>(1)</designum></desig></leg:heading>
<leg:levelbody>
<leg:bodytext>
<p><text>The testimony must have been taken:</text></p>
<l><li id="UCPN.OL.FOEA94.S22.1.A"><lilabel><refpt id="UCPN.OL.FOEA94.S22.1.A" type="ext"/>(a)</lilabel>
<p><text>on oath or affirmation; or</text></p>
</li>
<li id="UCPN.OL.FOEA94.S22.1.AA"><lilabel><refpt id="UCPN.OL.FOEA94.S22.1.AA" type="ext"/>(aa)</lilabel>
<p><text>under an obligation to tell the truth imposed, whether expressly or by implication, by or under a law of the foreign country concerned; or</text></p>
</li>
<li id="UCPN.OL.FOEA94.S22.1.B"><lilabel><refpt id="UCPN.OL.FOEA94.S22.1.B" type="ext"/>(b)</lilabel>
<p><text>under such caution or admonition as would be accepted, by courts in the foreign country concerned, for the purposes of giving testimony in proceedings before those courts.</text></p>
</li>
</l><leg:histnote>
<p><text>[subs (1)  am Act 55 of 2010  Sch 1[7], effective 4 June 2010]</text></p></leg:histnote>
</leg:bodytext>
</leg:levelbody>
</leg:level-vrnt>
</leg:level>
<leg:level id="UCPN.OL.FOEA94.S22.2"><leg:level-vrnt leveltype="subsect" searchtype="LEGISLATION SUBSECT">
<leg:levelinfo>
<leg:levelstatus isrepealed="false" ln.user-displayed="false"/></leg:levelinfo>
<leg:heading inline="true"><desig><designum><refpt id="UCPN.OL.FOEA94.S22.2" type="ext"/>(2)</designum></desig></leg:heading>
<leg:levelbody>
<leg:bodytext>
<p><text>The testimony must purport to be signed or certified by a judge, magistrate or officer in or of the foreign country to which the request was made.</text></p>
<leg:histnote>
<p><text>[subs (2)  subst Act 41 of 2003  sÂ 3 and Sch 2 , effective 3 June 2003]</text></p></leg:histnote>
</leg:bodytext>
</leg:levelbody>
</leg:level-vrnt>
</leg:level>
</leg:levelbody>
</leg:level-vrnt>
</leg:level>
<leg:level id="UCPN.OL.FOEA94.S23"><leg:level-vrnt leveltype="sect" searchtype="LEGISLATION SECT" subdoc="true" toc-caption="[320,250] s 23 Form of testimony">
<leg:levelinfo>
<leg:levelstatus isrepealed="false" ln.user-displayed="false"/></leg:levelinfo>
<leg:heading inline="true"><edpnum><refpt id="UCPN.OL.FOEA94.S23" type="ext"/>[320,250]</edpnum><title searchtype="SECT-TITLE">Form of testimony</title><desig searchtype="SECT-NUM"><designum>23</designum></desig></leg:heading>
<leg:levelbody>
<leg:level id="UCPN.OL.FOEA94.S23.1"><leg:level-vrnt leveltype="subsect" searchtype="LEGISLATION SUBSECT">
<leg:levelinfo>
<leg:levelstatus isrepealed="false" ln.user-displayed="false"/></leg:levelinfo>
<leg:heading inline="true"><desig><designum><refpt id="UCPN.OL.FOEA94.S23.1" type="ext"/>(1)</designum></desig></leg:heading>
<leg:levelbody>
<leg:bodytext>
<p><text>The testimony may be reduced to writing or be recorded on a tape, disk or other device from which sounds or images are capable of being reproduced.</text></p>
<leg:histnote>
<p><text>[subs (1)  am Act 55 of 2010  Sch 1[8], effective 4 June 2010]</text></p></leg:histnote>
</leg:bodytext>
</leg:levelbody>
</leg:level-vrnt>
</leg:level>
<leg:level id="UCPN.OL.FOEA94.S23.2"><leg:level-vrnt leveltype="subsect" searchtype="LEGISLATION SUBSECT">
<leg:levelinfo>
<leg:levelstatus isrepealed="false" ln.user-displayed="false"/></leg:levelinfo>
<leg:heading inline="true"><desig><designum><refpt id="UCPN.OL.FOEA94.S23.2" type="ext"/>(2)</designum></desig></leg:heading>
<leg:levelbody>
<leg:bodytext>
<p><text>The testimony need not:</text></p>
<l><li id="UCPN.OL.FOEA94.S23.2.A"><lilabel><refpt id="UCPN.OL.FOEA94.S23.2.A" type="ext"/>(a)</lilabel>
<p><text>be in the form of an affidavit; or</text></p>
</li>
<li id="UCPN.OL.FOEA94.S23.2.B"><lilabel><refpt id="UCPN.OL.FOEA94.S23.2.B" type="ext"/>(b)</lilabel>
<p><text>constitute a transcript of a proceeding in a foreign court.</text></p>
</li>
</l>
</leg:bodytext>
</leg:levelbody>
</leg:level-vrnt>
</leg:level>
</leg:levelbody>
</leg:level-vrnt>
</leg:level>
</leg:levelbody>
</leg:level-vrnt>
</leg:level></leg:levelbody></leg:level-vrnt></leg:level></leg:levelbody></leg:level-vrnt></leg:level></leg:body></LEGDOC>